f","type":"paragraph","text":"他病态的自尊心已经再经不住损伤。","index":89,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"1a9c2ccc57","type":"paragraph","text":"这时候，科员又悄悄来到身傍，","index":90,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"3939d65306","type":"paragraph","text":"“依我看，咱们的问题不一定讲，","index":91,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"3d84d433f3","type":"paragraph","text":"上级本来对咱有偏见，","index":92,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"14dc741e87","type":"paragraph","text":"这一次可不敢再添坏印象；","index":93,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"a0739236af","type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的总结应该讲点‘策略’，","index":94,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"cf714df993","type":"paragraph","text":"把发生的毛病来一个‘捉迷藏’。”","index":95,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"f00e00f99c","type":"paragraph","text":"这位科长默默无言，","index":96,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"c81681468d","type":"paragraph","text":"他没有指令科员去写假报告，","index":97,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"e80b277613","type":"paragraph","text":"但是经他签了字送上的总结，","index":98,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"381cd1571c","type":"paragraph","text":"满纸是虚报成绩的撒谎。","index":99,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"63d61b29df","type":"paragraph","text":"从此以后，科员钻进了科长的“肝脏”，","index":100,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"297cff690f","type":"paragraph","text":"大事小事科长都要找科员商量；","index":101,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"871cdc4b94","type":"paragraph","text":"国家机密，党内文件，","index":102,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"21bfceca45","type":"paragraph","text":"科员的口袋变成了保险箱。","index":103,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"642d0c8326"},{"id":"1c3526c2a3","type":"paragraph","text":"机关的工作和生活忽然变得希奇古怪，","index":104,"publicationI